        {
            "title": "你好，打劫！Reunion丨張家輝、魯文傑後台敘舊暢聊往事 AL讚嘆演員2小時完成高強度舞台",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"你好，打劫！Reunion丨張家輝、魯文傑後台敘舊暢聊往事 AL讚嘆演員2小時完成高強度舞台\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9ae8aa74e4b996a28c8650b5aa862ee1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051616315521291.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">你好，打劫！Reunion丨張家輝、魯文傑後台敘舊暢聊往事 AL讚嘆演員2小時完成高強度舞台</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>由朱栢康、魯文傑、麥沛東、芯駖@COLLAR等主演，朱栢謙、張志敏擔執導、鄧永威監製、劉德華出品的舞台劇《你好，打劫！Reunion》，12場演出至昨晚（15號）已公演第8場，繼續座無虛席，台前台後同樣精彩，連夜來圈中不少友好捧包括：張家輝、袁富華、謝君豪、盧瀚霆（Anson Lo)、李凱賢@24味、肥仔梁業、193郭嘉駿、導演陳茂賢、梁雍婷、余安安、鍾雪瑩、呂良偉等。\n\n</p><h2>AL未有想過演舞台劇</h2>\n<p>《你好，打劫！Reunion》2度香港公演，加入新陣容，重新改編後，令觀眾看得更透徹，節奏控制明快，比上次更有質感，大家對劇中不少笑點位留下深刻印象，尤其對首次演出舞台劇的芯駖大感意外驚喜。朱栢康solo演出拍案叫絕，麥沛東、魯文傑同様是水準之上，2小時的演出讓觀眾看得過癮。昨晚Anson Lo單拖到場撐老友麥沛東、朱栢康、芯駖，看罷整場演出後，也讚嘆他們2小時演出精彩之餘，尤其體力的應付真的很強勁，至於自己可有心癢也想演舞台劇？在場偷師的他笑說：「我睇吓已經夠㗎啦!佢哋嘅體能真係好勁，兩個鐘頭完全冇離開過個舞台。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo、魯文𠎀、麥沛東\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af3a7db25c84b0a864d0fac364cc8d1b/2025-05/Anson_Lo_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo、魯文𠎀、麥沛東\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"余安安都有現身。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d143eda4a4f3f67a8b086dd7693c0914/2025-05/IMG_0382.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        余安安都有現身。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo單拖到場撐老友麥沛東、朱栢康、芯駖。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/35e8613a6220e5094dbceba475285f2b/2025-05/IMG_0383.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo單拖到場撐老友麥沛東、朱栢康、芯駖。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"AL讚嘆演員們2小時演出精彩之餘，尤其體力的應付真的很強勁。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a256ae58a7c966629ed655d5b3c4ec3b/2025-05/IMG_0386.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        AL讚嘆演員們2小時演出精彩之餘，尤其體力的應付真的很強勁。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"AL與芯駖selfie。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8ad4daeda92d16f9dfe347f8d48cf592/2025-05/IMG_0388.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        AL與芯駖selfie。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"《破地獄》導演陳茂賢支持朱柏康。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6ff325bc8e13a16cdc6fae96725ad31b/2025-05/IMG_9912.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《破地獄》導演陳茂賢支持朱柏康。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Error肥仔\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57a3c72ab030d9e5d73a4d545d274619/2025-05/IMG_9934.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Error肥仔\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"張家輝的現身讓大家大感驚喜。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4474f1461d7225c871484f94c43ef2d/2025-05/174738397928654.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張家輝的現身讓大家大感驚喜。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家輝與一眾演員在後台合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/543f0bf3b24a4e453f66716e32cdb2e2/2025-05/174738397952879.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家輝與一眾演員在後台合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"樂隊24味與團隊成員合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ba0e62b017bb427ec1a91e4a8074795a/2025-05/24_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        樂隊24味與團隊成員合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"一眾舞台劇帝（謝君豪、朱栢康、魯文傑）雲集，現場氣勢磅礡。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8ad10177dc8f2c9e13278cee0f517e8b/2025-05/174738397923898.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一眾舞台劇帝（謝君豪、朱栢康、魯文傑）雲集，現場氣勢磅礡。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>張家輝與魯文傑敘舊</h2>\n<p>至於早兩晚現身後台為一眾演員打氣的張家輝，讓大家大感驚喜，難得到場大家合照留念之餘，家輝也趁機與當年在電視劇《十萬噸情緣》的魯文傑敘舊，聊往事氣氛溫馨。這陣子忙為舞台劇作準備的謝君豪，也抽空到場欣賞，完場後還到後台探班，一眾舞台劇帝（謝君豪、朱栢康、魯文傑）雲集，令現場氣勢磅礡，台前台後一樣充滿「戲」味。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
